{
  "stem": "1975.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So with the way we knew is, we didn't have communication but we had, like, mouth-to-mouth communication, where the Lithuanians would come-- some of them who had friends who were-- there were exceptions to the rule.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were some Lithuanians who were very friendly with some of the people, and they really felt for them, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they-- they were the ones that told us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- and the people who lived in-- in-- surrounding the fort, they heard shooting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and then they had to bury them, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They used to dig out mass graves with a bulldozer, and they used to bury them there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Were there work details?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- right away they instituted-- you know, the biggest concern of theirs and what they needed right away to do is to put back the airport in-- in the-- in good condition so they can use that for the Luftwaffe, you know.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the first brigades, working brigades, that were instituted were the-- to the airport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had to work-- to go to work to the airport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If somebody was sick or he didn't feel good, he had to find somebody else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like I, for instance, I at that time-- this was 1941, and I was 17 at that time, so I worked for myself.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My uncle was a sick man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- I used to work a second shift, which was, like, 10 hours, another 10 hours to work for my uncle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a-- we had to walk under guard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was, like, eight, nine miles to the airport, back and forth, about 18 miles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And ration was very meager.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had, like, a piece-- 200 grams of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
